line-height.semantic-desc:
It is recommended to keep consistency with font size semantics.
Example: If the font size definition includes { "title": "24px" },
the corresponding line height semantic definition should be { "title-xs": "24px", "title-sm": "28px", "title-md": "32px" }

weight.semantic-desc:
It is recommended to keep consistency with font size semantics.
Example: If the font size definition includes { "text": "14px", "title": "24px" },
the corresponding font weight semantic definition should be { "text": "400", "title": "700" }
